I had taken him for a walk along the corridors and he collapsed three times.

41:30.662 --> 41:32.704
He was very, very ill that week after this.

41:36.128 --> 41:37.910
And, you know, I was on my own in the corridor.

41:37.930 --> 41:38.971
It was really difficult.

41:39.051 --> 41:39.592
But anyway,

